3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - Recommender systems are a popular application of AI, and the paper discusses a new approach to improve their accuracy. 
4. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - Recommender systems are often used in social networks, and the paper discusses their development in the era of socialized web.
